<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.332207, "shard": "07", "shelf_id": "sn85066387, 1908-05-17, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/curiv", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["san francisco (calif.)", "san francisco bay area", "san francisco", "california", "newspapers", "san francisco bay area (calif.)", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["San Francisco (Calif.)--Newspapers", "San Francisco Bay Area (Calif.)--Newspapers", "California--San Francisco", "California--San Francisco Bay Area", "United States--California--San Francisco--San Francisco"], "subjects": [{"california": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:california&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"san francisco": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:san+francisco&fo=json"}, {"san francisco (calif.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:san+francisco+%28calif.%29&fo=json"}, {"san francisco bay area": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:san+francisco+bay+area&fo=json"}, {"san francisco bay area (calif.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:san+francisco+bay+area+%28calif.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2025-09-28T21:21:57.165Z", "title": "The San Francisco call (San Francisco [Calif.]), May 17, 1908", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn85066387/1908-05-17/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85066387/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn85066387", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/3f52bd2a-1efc-5176-9f28-f045044852ea"], "batch": ["curiv_ahwahnee_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1895", "description": ["Daily Vol. 77, no. 85 (Mar. 5, 1895)-v. 115, no. 7 (Dec. 8, 1913). \"San Francisco\" appears above, and later across, masthead ornament. Publishers: Charles M. Shortridge, <1896>; John D. Spreckles, <1899>. Also issued online. Master negatives are available for duplication from: California Newspaper Microfilm Archive; for further information consult the CNMA at: http://cbsr.ucr.edu. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Issued with a joint ed. of the San Francisco chronicle and the San Francisco examiner on the day after the San Francisco earthquake, Apr. 19, 1906. San Francisco evening post (DLC)sn 94052992 (OCoLC)31898483 San Francisco call and post (DLC)sn 86064451 (OCoLC)13146198"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:16.241Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-12", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-12"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85066387/", "image_url": [], "index": 25, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [37.7800771, -122.4201615], "location": ["san francisco bay area", "san francisco", "united states", "california"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-122.4201615, 37.7800771], "number": ["new york pub libr res libr", "microfilm master", "microfilm service copy", "california hist soc", "1941-0719", "san francisco pub libr", "haggin mus, the", "abraham lincoln presidential libr", "sn86064451", "sacramento arch & mus, mcclatchy collect", "county of los angeles pub libr", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "oakland pub libr", "1", "sn8506